			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://theatre-of-the-air.com/WordPress/wp-content/uploads/2008/08/sbta-blog2.gif" ><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-69" title="sbta-blog2" src="http://theatre-of-the-air.com/WordPress/wp-content/uploads/2008/08/sbta-blog2.gif" alt="" width="223" height="275" /></a></p>
